        "language_name": "english",
        "name": ""
      },
      "text": "<div class=ar lang=ar><p><span class=\"qpc-hafs\">﴿إنَّ الإنْسان﴾</span> الجِنْس <span class=\"qpc-hafs\">﴿لَفِي خُسْر﴾</span> فِي تِجارَته</p></div>",
      "verses": {
